  <license uri="http://www.php.net/license">PHP License</license>
  
  <notes>
  * Added Callback Support for objects
  * Changed the parsing engine for a tree based parser
  * Apparent Functionnalities should not be changed
  * API changes should come shortly
	New features to be exposed:
	  - Tags automatic reopen, in order to produce
		Valid HTML, consistent Visual output with invalid BBCode
	  - Enhanced parser optionnal rules.
  </notes>

